Breakfast in bed at 6pm?! Because... why not?! -

On the menu today... -

Main: Sautéed shrooms, spinach, tomato and green capsicum on homemade kamut bread, garnished with caramelised onions 🍴🍞 -

Beverage: Hot matcha dark choco made with our “THE ALL-IN-ONE HEALTH ELIXIR” 80% dark choco w Uji matcha and coconut milk 🤤🍫☕️ -

Dessert: Our matcha choco mmm 😋🍫 -

Can anyone guess the film I watched today?? And.... watch me cook on IG stories!!! 👩🏻‍🍳 What did y’all do today? 🤗
love breakfast anytime of the day 💚
Wow😍 you really know how to treat yourself. How was the taste? Good luck with your Instagram journey🌱💪
